    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Honestly, I\u2019m a bit sad to see this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it. This car is in absolutely pristine, showroom-level condition\u2014it's been kept in a garage and babied since day one. Not a scratch or a dent to be found! It drives like a dream and still has that new-car feel. If you\u2019re looking for a total gem that\u2019s been loved every mile, this is the one for you. Come take a look and see for yourself!",
      "price": 44900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
