    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true collector-grade example, meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled environment since day one. The exterior features a factory-perfect finish with a deep, mirror-like luster, protected by a high-end ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom condition; the premium leather seats show absolutely no bolster wear, and the original protective films are still present on several interior components. Mechanically, the car is flawless, having followed a rigorous preventative maintenance schedule with all records organized and available. It drives exactly as it did the day it left the dealership\u2014tight, responsive, and exceptionally smooth. This is a rare opportunity to own a virtually new vehicle that has been treated with the utmost reverence.",
      "price": 48500.0,
